00:32:19,400 --> 00:32:20,100
 i to ti je dosta.

582
00:32:20,100 --> 00:32:22,820
 Ali mi ni to ne prihvaćamo.

583
00:32:22,820 --> 00:32:25,360
 A zašto ti je onda tako teško

584
00:32:25,360 --> 00:32:26,940
 ženi biti milosrni?

585
00:32:26,940 --> 00:32:27,660
 Kad ona pogriješi,

586
00:32:27,660 --> 00:32:28,420
 pa budi ko krist,

587
00:32:28,420 --> 00:32:29,420
 opravdaju,

588
00:32:29,420 --> 00:32:30,600
 ohrabrije,

589
00:32:30,600 --> 00:32:31,560
 podignije,

590
00:32:31,560 --> 00:32:33,360
 budi joj blizu,

591
00:32:33,360 --> 00:32:34,620
 nemoj nabijat krivnju,

592
00:32:34,620 --> 00:32:36,600
 nemoj raditi ono što se to

593
00:32:36,600 --> 00:32:37,820
 naradi nama cijelo vrijeme.

594
00:32:37,820 --> 00:32:39,500
 Budi joj milosrdan.

595
00:32:40,300 --> 00:32:41,700
 Jer kad ćeš spuštat milost

596
00:32:41,700 --> 00:32:42,500
 u svoj brak,

597
00:32:42,500 --> 00:32:44,440
 onda napokon može došt

598
00:32:44,440 --> 00:32:44,940
 do odnosa.

599
00:32:44,940 --> 00:32:46,340
 Jer nema odnosa u krivnji.

600
00:32:46,340 --> 00:32:48,440
 Jer u krivnji neko mora biti kriv

601
00:32:48,440 --> 00:32:49,600
 i taj ide upakao,

602
00:32:49,600 --> 00:32:50,020
 taj je kriv,

603
00:32:50,020 --> 00:32:50,700
 taj nije dobar,

604
00:32:50,700 --> 00:32:52,620
 a Isusu najmanji problem

605
00:32:52,620 --> 00:32:53,140
 ko je kriv.

606
00:32:53,140 --> 00:32:54,220
 Ja do čak i na gradlištu

607
00:32:54,220 --> 00:32:55,120
 objašnjavam svojim dečkima.

608
00:32:55,120 --> 00:32:55,900
 Dečki nema veze

609
00:32:55,900 --> 00:32:56,640
 ko je pogriješio.

610
00:32:56,640 --> 00:32:58,260
 Radimo istu zgradu.

611
00:32:58,260 --> 00:32:59,500
 Jer si ti sad njega

612
00:32:59,500 --> 00:33:00,360
 zeznok električar

613
00:33:00,360 --> 00:33:01,680
 ili ti njega prešao

614
00:33:01,680 --> 00:33:02,320
 s tijema prvi

615
00:33:02,320 --> 00:33:03,060
 kovo da je instalater.

616
00:33:03,500 --> 00:33:04,680
 Radimo isti projekt, dečki.

617
00:33:04,680 --> 00:33:05,900
 Meni nije bitno ko je kriv.

618
00:33:05,900 --> 00:33:08,520
 Zajedno idemo došt do rješenja.

619
00:33:08,520 --> 00:33:09,920
 To je ista stvar u braku

620
00:33:09,920 --> 00:33:11,360
 i bilo kojem drugom području.

621
00:33:11,360 --> 00:33:12,520
 Najmanja je,

622
00:33:12,520 --> 00:33:14,280
 Isusu je najmanji mogući projem

623
00:33:14,280 --> 00:33:14,700
 ko je kriv.

624
00:33:14,700 --> 00:33:15,120
 On kaže,

625
00:33:15,120 --> 00:33:16,300
 dečki, cure,

626
00:33:16,300 --> 00:33:17,960
 ja vam greke bacam na dnomora.

627
00:33:17,960 --> 00:33:19,680
 Mene ne interesiraju vaše grijesi.

628
00:33:19,680 --> 00:33:20,740
 Mene interesiraš ti.

629
00:33:20,740 --> 00:33:23,780
 Meni si važan samo ti.

630
00:33:23,780 --> 00:33:25,040
 Kad se pokaješ,

631
00:33:25,040 --> 00:33:26,740
 grijeh ne postoji.

632
00:33:26,740 --> 00:33:28,840
 A mi grijeh uvijek u centar.

633
00:33:28,840 --> 00:33:30,340
 Uvijek stavi ga da ga svi vide

634
00:33:30,340 --> 00:33:32,600
 u smislu da drugo ga obtužimo,

635
00:33:33,120 --> 00:33:35,100
 da ono baš pokažem ono.

636
00:33:35,100 --> 00:33:37,040
 A svako od nas kad pogriješi,

637
00:33:37,040 --> 00:33:38,580
 ono zna da je pogriješio.

638
00:33:38,580 --> 00:33:40,240
 Znaš se, uvijek pogriješio sam.

639
00:33:40,240 --> 00:33:41,700
 I onda kad je onaj drugi

640
00:33:41,700 --> 00:33:43,020
 još ono stavi to na ploču,

641
00:33:43,020 --> 00:33:44,300
 svi je ono on je pogriješio.

642
00:33:44,300 --> 00:33:46,220
 Pa kom je to ikad pomoglo?

643
00:33:46,220 --> 00:33:48,260
 Ko se je ikad promijenio

644
00:33:48,260 --> 00:33:49,340
 kad te neko još drugi

645
00:33:49,340 --> 00:33:50,500
 još dodatno ponizi

646
00:33:50,500 --> 00:33:51,560
 ili kad si dobio jedan u školi

647
00:33:51,560 --> 00:33:52,960
 pa te još dobiješ doma

648
00:33:52,960 --> 00:33:54,040
 ono batine i nešto

649
00:33:54,040 --> 00:33:55,400
 i onda još izinato uvijek.

650
00:33:55,400 --> 00:33:57,220
 Samo možeš stvoriti

651
00:33:57,220 --> 00:33:58,600
 još dodatne rane i probleme

652
00:33:58,600 --> 00:33:59,380
 ne zna šta drugo.

653
00:33:59,380 --> 00:34:01,960
 Dakle, ako želiš biti svet u braku

654
00:34:01,960 --> 00:34:02,800
 budi milosrdan.

655
00:34:02,800 --> 00:34:04,420
 Jer naš otac je milosrdan.

656
00:34:04,420 --> 00:34:06,680
 Papa Franjo donosio tu revoluciju

657
00:34:06,680 --> 00:34:07,840
 milosrdja.

658
00:34:07,840 --> 00:34:09,080
 I drugi su ga obtuživali

659
00:34:09,080 --> 00:34:11,440
 jer mi katolici ne volimo milosrdja.

660
00:34:11,960 --> 00:34:13,700
 nas potiče krivnja

661
00:34:13,700 --> 00:34:14,880
 mene poticala krivnja.

662
00:34:14,880 --> 00:34:17,300
 Ja kad sam htio služiti u zajednici

663
00:34:17,300 --> 00:34:18,980
 ja sam mislio da me Bog neće voljet

664
00:34:18,980 --> 00:34:20,320
 ako ja ne služim

665
00:34:20,320 --> 00:34:21,300
 ako ja ne radim

666
00:34:21,300 --> 00:34:22,520
 ako ja ne zaslužim ljubav.

667
00:34:22,520 --> 00:34:24,420
 I onda mi živcirala milost.

668
00:34:24,420 --> 00:34:25,860
 Zašto ovaj tamo

669
00:34:25,860 --> 00:34:26,340
 ono

670
00:34:26,340 --> 00:34:27,900
 Bog mu se smiluje meni

671
00:34:27,900 --> 00:34:29,060
 ja moram raditi

672
00:34:29,060 --> 00:34:30,100
 ono ko taj stariji sin.

673
00:34:30,100 --> 00:34:30,720
 Zato što mi

674
00:34:30,720 --> 00:34:32,180
 katolici nažalost

675
00:34:32,180 --> 00:34:33,440
 ono duže taj duh

676
00:34:33,440 --> 00:34:35,360
 religioznosti

677
00:34:35,360 --> 00:34:36,960
 i ja moram zaslužiti

678
00:34:36,960 --> 00:34:37,660
 ja moram raditi

679
00:34:37,660 --> 00:34:39,280
 a šta moraš raditi

680
00:34:39,280 --> 00:34:40,700
 kad je on sve za tebe napravio

681
00:34:40,700 --> 00:34:41,820
 za mu se prepusti.

682
00:34:41,960 --> 00:34:44,140
 Nemoj razmišljati o grijehu

683
00:34:44,140 --> 00:34:45,420
 razmišljaj o gospodinu

684
00:34:45,420 --> 00:34:46,920
 hrani se Božem riječu

685
00:34:46,920 --> 00:34:47,740
 razmatraj

686
00:34:47,740 --> 00:34:49,100
 gledaj njegova čudesa

687
00:34:49,100 --> 00:34:50,140
 silinu, ljepotu

688
00:34:50,140 --> 00:34:51,640
 i šta moraš više raditi.

689
00:34:51,640 --> 00:34:52,920
 Uživaj u tom odnosu.

690
00:34:52,920 --> 00:34:55,700
 Dakle, ako ćeš biti svet u braku

691
00:34:55,700 --> 00:34:56,580
 budi milosrdan.

692
00:34:56,580 --> 00:35:04,580
 Treće

693
00:35:04,580 --> 00:35:07,120
 kako biti svet u ljubavi.

694
00:35:07,120 --> 00:35:09,580
 Ovdje je važno za naglasiti

695
00:35:09,580 --> 00:35:12,760
 ono kad profesor priča o svom predmetu

696
00:35:12,760 --> 00:35:13,260
 o meni je ovo

697
00:35:13,260 --> 00:35:15,040
 zanimacija zadnjih par godina

698
00:35:15,040 --> 00:35:16,540
 brak, veze, obitelj

699
00:35:16,540 --> 00:35:17,100
 onda znaju reću

700
00:35:17,100 --> 00:35:17,920
 a to je najvažnije.

701
00:35:17,920 --> 00:35:19,540
 Da nema braka, ne je bilo svijeta

702
00:35:19,540 --> 00:35:20,240
 ne je bilo ničega

703
00:35:20,240 --> 00:35:21,440
 morate naučiti brak

704
00:35:21,440 --> 00:35:22,220
 to je najvažnije.

705
00:35:22,220 --> 00:35:24,280
 Brak nije cilj samo sebi

706
00:35:24,280 --> 00:35:25,140
 ja sam loš profesor.

707
00:35:25,140 --> 00:35:26,940
 Brak nije centar svijeta.

708
00:35:26,940 --> 00:35:28,720
 Brak je samo put

709
00:35:28,720 --> 00:35:30,940
 odnosno hod našeg posvećenja

710
00:35:30,940 --> 00:35:31,760
 ko nas priprema

711
00:35:31,760 --> 00:35:33,260
 i koji je savršeno stvoren

712
00:35:33,260 --> 00:35:34,160
 i posložen

713
00:35:34,160 --> 00:35:34,760
 da nas dovede

714
00:35:34,760 --> 00:35:35,420
 do svetosti.

715
00:35:35,420 --> 00:35:37,040
 On ne smije biti cilj.

716
00:35:37,040 --> 00:35:39,000
 Jer Isus se kaže

717
00:35:39,000 --> 00:35:40,520
 u nebu nema ženi

718
00:35:40,520 --> 00:35:41,940
 nećemo se više ženi tu davati.

719
00:35:41,940 --> 00:35:44,260
 Uženit ćeš se kao zaručnica

720
00:35:44,260 --> 00:35:45,300
 svako od nas

721
00:35:45,300 --> 00:35:46,700
 mi kao crkva s Kristom.

722
00:35:46,700 --> 00:35:48,860
 Zato ti gore ne treba više žena

723
00:35:48,860 --> 00:35:49,400
 u smislu

724
00:35:49,400 --> 00:35:50,660
 tijelesnom.

725
00:35:50,660 --> 00:35:50,880
 Jer

726
00:35:50,880 --> 00:35:53,700
 dođi ćeš do punine.

727
00:35:53,700 --> 00:35:54,940
 Znači gledat ćeš lice mu lice.

728
00:35:54,940 --> 00:35:56,940
 Sad živimo u slici

729
00:35:56,940 --> 00:35:58,320
 a u onaj trenutak

730
00:35:58,320 --> 00:35:59,360
 ćemo gledati lice mu lice.

731
00:35:59,360 --> 00:36:01,080
 Dakle vjenčanje je slika

732
00:36:01,080 --> 00:36:03,200
 odnosa

733
00:36:03,200 --> 00:36:04,400
 i vjenčanja

734
00:36:04,400 --> 00:36:06,980
 zaručnice crkve s Kristom.

735
00:36:06,980 --> 00:36:08,360
 I kad dođeš u nebo

736
00:36:08,360 --> 00:36:09,440
 to je cilj.

737
00:36:09,440 --> 00:36:10,720
 To je ono što mi svi

738
00:36:10,720 --> 00:36:12,120
 borimo se

739
00:36:12,120 --> 00:36:14,080
 za čime svi čeznamo

740
00:36:14,080 --> 00:36:14,940
 i što svi želimo.

741
00:36:14,940 --> 00:36:16,440
 Tako da

742
00:36:16,440 --> 00:36:18,800
 nemojmo se zatvoriti

743
00:36:18,800 --> 00:36:19,540
 u svoj brak

744
00:36:19,540 --> 00:36:20,760
 nego se otvorimo

745
00:36:20,760 --> 00:36:21,460
 jer je

746
00:36:21,460 --> 00:36:23,800
 mi smo kao crkva zaručnica

747
00:36:23,800 --> 00:36:25,940
 i nećemo

748
00:36:25,940 --> 00:36:27,100
 svaki pojedinačno

749
00:36:27,100 --> 00:36:27,780
 se spašavati

750
00:36:27,780 --> 00:36:28,000
 nego

751
00:36:28,000 --> 00:36:29,480
 baš upravo kao zajednica.

752
00:36:29,480 --> 00:36:30,680
 Brak te prvo tome uči

753
00:36:30,680 --> 00:36:31,800
 i nemoj se zatvoriti

754
00:36:31,800 --> 00:36:32,320
 u svoj brak

755
00:36:32,320 --> 00:36:32,680
 jer opet

756
00:36:32,680 --> 00:36:34,120
 onda si kao pojedinac.

757
00:36:34,120 --> 00:36:35,820
 Otvorite se u zajednicu

758
00:36:35,820 --> 00:36:36,520
 i ja volim

759
00:36:36,520 --> 00:36:38,100
 na našim grupama reći

760
00:36:38,100 --> 00:36:39,380
 nećete uspjeti sami

761
00:36:39,380 --> 00:36:41,200
 čak ni sami u braku.

762
00:36:41,200 --> 00:36:42,900
 Morate se otvoriti zajednici

763
00:36:42,900 --> 00:36:43,680
 ili župnoj

764
00:36:43,680 --> 00:36:45,440
 ili bilo kojoj drugoj

765
00:36:45,440 --> 00:36:46,100
 u blizini

766
00:36:46,100 --> 00:36:46,620
 ili idite

767
00:36:46,620 --> 00:36:48,420
 kak treba i sto kilometara dalje

768
00:36:48,420 --> 00:36:51,000
 ali nećete preživjeti u zajednici.

769
00:36:51,000 --> 00:36:52,440
 Nećete preživjeti sami.

770
00:36:52,440 --> 00:36:53,640
 Morate se priključiti

771
00:36:53,640 --> 00:36:54,380
 u nekoj zajednici.

772
00:36:54,380 --> 00:36:55,600
 Jer crkva je zajednica

773
00:36:55,600 --> 00:36:56,720
 crkva nije pojedinac.

774
00:36:56,720 --> 00:36:58,400
 Isus nije umro za jednoga.

775
00:36:58,400 --> 00:37:00,400
 On je umro za svoju crkvu

776
00:37:00,400 --> 00:37:01,520
 i kad god govori

777
00:37:01,520 --> 00:37:01,900
 on govori

778
00:37:01,900 --> 00:37:03,820
 da je za crkvu to sve napravio.

779
00:37:05,380 --> 00:37:07,840
 Tako da cilj je da mi svi kao crkva

780
00:37:07,840 --> 00:37:09,600
 budemo spašeni.

781
00:37:09,600 --> 00:37:10,920
 U braku se to učimo.

782
00:37:10,920 --> 00:37:14,320
 I sad ono što mi volimo govoriti

783
00:37:14,320 --> 00:37:15,640
 na našem tečaju je da

784
00:37:15,640 --> 00:37:18,460
 Krista uključimo u brak.

785
00:37:18,460 --> 00:37:20,460
 I kako to Krista uključiti u brak?

786
00:37:20,460 --> 00:37:22,180
 Pa u tvoje ženi je Krist.

787
00:37:22,180 --> 00:37:24,400
 I sad kad se ti

788
00:37:24,400 --> 00:37:25,920
 ponašaš loše prema ženi

789
00:37:25,920 --> 00:37:27,000
 ti to činiš Kristu.

790
00:37:28,000 --> 00:37:30,740
 I već smo više puta spominjali

791
00:37:30,740 --> 00:37:32,040
 jedan od glavnih božih

792
00:37:32,040 --> 00:37:36,680
 alata, prioriteta, načela, šta god

793
00:37:36,680 --> 00:37:38,240
 je da od malih se stvari

794
00:37:38,240 --> 00:37:39,240
 sve kreće raditi.

795
00:37:39,240 --> 00:37:42,120
 I moja žena, moji sakrament

796
00:37:42,120 --> 00:37:43,880
 i ajmo reći jedna od tih malih stvari.

797
00:37:43,880 --> 00:37:47,120
 I način na koji se ja ponašam

798
00:37:47,120 --> 00:37:48,220
 prema svojim Mihaeli

799
00:37:48,220 --> 00:37:50,440
 je način na koji se ponašam prema Kristu.

800
00:37:50,440 --> 00:37:52,720
 I onog dana kad ja dođem na posljedni sud

801
00:37:52,720 --> 00:37:54,360
 kad stanem pred Krista

802
00:37:54,360 --> 00:37:55,760
 on neće govoriti

803
00:37:55,760 --> 00:37:57,520
 o bravo Matej vodio si zajednicu

804
00:37:57,520 --> 00:37:59,680
 ti si govorio na konferenciji

805
00:37:59,680 --> 00:38:00,820
 ti si super

806
00:38:00,820 --> 00:38:01,640
 ti si postio

807
00:38:01,640 --> 00:38:02,120
 ti si molio

808
00:38:02,120 --> 00:38:03,420
 on će reći

809
00:38:03,420 --> 00:38:04,920
 kak si se ponašao prema Meli

810
00:38:04,920 --> 00:38:05,820
 kroz Mihaelu?

811
00:38:05,820 --> 00:38:07,780
 Jesi optuživao?

812
00:38:07,780 --> 00:38:08,780
 Jesi bio grub?

813
00:38:08,780 --> 00:38:10,500
 Jesi molio za nju?

814
00:38:10,500 --> 00:38:12,900
 Šta si radio?

815
00:38:12,900 --> 00:38:15,180
 Ako si takav bio prema njoj

816
00:38:15,180 --> 00:38:16,340
 neizinteresiran

817
00:38:16,340 --> 00:38:17,160
 gledao samo sebe

818
00:38:17,160 --> 00:38:17,860
 bio sebičan

819
00:38:17,860 --> 00:38:19,740
 pa ti nemaš šta raditi u mom kraljevstvu.

820
00:38:19,740 --> 00:38:21,940
 Ako toj jednoj ljepoj ženi

821
00:38:21,940 --> 00:38:22,820
 koju sam ti dao

822
00:38:22,820 --> 00:38:23,760
 ti nisi znao

823
00:38:23,760 --> 00:38:24,940
 tu je pred tobom vidljiva

824
00:38:24,940 --> 00:38:25,820
 znači ja nisam vidljiva

825
00:38:25,820 --> 00:38:26,540
 ona je vidljiva.

826
00:38:27,040 --> 00:38:28,360
 Ako ti ne znaš njoj to raditi

827
00:38:28,360 --> 00:38:29,760
 pa šta ti imaš raditi u mom kraljevstvu?

828
00:38:29,760 --> 00:38:30,960
 Pa šta mi treba takav jedan

829
00:38:30,960 --> 00:38:32,240
 mlakonjak od ti

830
00:38:32,240 --> 00:38:35,000
 koji nisi dostojan

831
00:38:35,000 --> 00:38:36,400
 pokazati ljubav ženi

832
00:38:36,400 --> 00:38:37,500
 koju sam ti rekao

833
00:38:37,500 --> 00:38:38,440
 da je pokažeš ljubav

834
00:38:38,440 --> 00:38:39,260
 koju si obećao?

835
00:38:39,260 --> 00:38:40,620
 Nije nas niko tjerano na ženi.

836
00:38:40,620 --> 00:38:42,280
 Pa sami smo obećali, potpisali.

837
00:38:42,280 --> 00:38:44,240
 Rekli ja ću ljubiti

838
00:38:44,240 --> 00:38:45,760
 i poštivati do kraja života.

839
00:38:46,900 --> 00:38:48,460
 I ako ti taj savez ne ispoštuješ

840
00:38:48,460 --> 00:38:49,240
 pa zašto bi Isus

841
00:38:49,240 --> 00:38:51,140
